OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,FThe Stormont Assembly is set to be
OL,7,Fchallenged to commit to reform to
OL,8,Fprevent future collapses during the
OL,9,Ffirst official Opposition day.
OL,11,FOpposition leader Matthew O'Toole has
OL,12,Fproposed three motions calling for a
OL,13,Fcommitment to reform the institutions
OL,14,Fin the Programme for Government and an
OL,15,Fad hoc committee to consider
OL,16,Flegislation to prevent further
OL,17,Fcollapses.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/14
