PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F445A1709620311
OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,FThe first motion also calls for an
OL,7,Fapology to public sector workers for
OL,8,Fyears of suspension, and another
OL,9,Fmotion calls for the swift resolution
OL,10,Fto pay negotiations for those workers
OL,11,Fwho staged a major strike in January.
OL,13,FMr O'Toole described the motions as a
OL,14,F"real test of how serious all parties
OL,15,Fare about, not just the principle, but
OL,16,Fdelivering on reform", and expressing
OL,17,Fregret.
