OL,6,FIt will be the first Opposition day at
OL,7,FStormont in recent years following the
OL,8,Fdecision by the SDLP to go into
OL,9,FOpposition.
OL,11,FThe SDLP and UUP previously formed an
OL,12,Fofficial Opposition in 2016, however
OL,13,Fthis came to an end in January 2017
OL,14,Fwhen then deputy first minister Martin
OL,15,FMcGuinness resigned, effectively
OL,16,Fcollapsing the institutions until 2020.
