OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,FThe Assembly was revived in January
OL,7,Fafter two years of disruption
OL,8,Ffollowing the resignation of then
OL,9,Ffirst minister Paul Givan as part of
OL,10,Fthe DUP's protest at post-Brexit
OL,11,Ftrading arrangements.
OL,13,FMr O'Toole told the PA news agency
OL,14,Fthat parties expressing regret over
OL,15,Fthe political instability and
OL,16,Fcommitting to reform would mark a
OL,17,F"milestone where we move on to
OL,18,Fsomething more sustainable from veto
OL,19,Fand stalemate".
