OL,6,FMr O'Toole said those suspensions led
OL,7,Fto public services "falling to the
OL,8,Fworst state in western Europe in some
OL,9,Fcases, particularly the health
OL,10,Fservice".
OL,12,F"That is why our first Opposition day
OL,13,Fis focused squarely on reform of the
OL,14,Finstitutions, reforming how Stormont
OL,15,Fworks so this can't happen again," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
