OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,F"We're not just setting out
OL,7,Faspirations. This is about actually
OL,8,Fgetting binding commitments and a
OL,9,Fprocess in place to stop Stormont ever
OL,10,Fcollapsing again. Reforming the rules
OL,11,Fso that veto cannot be used to
OL,12,Fcollapse government again.
OL,14,F"We also have a motion on public
OL,15,Fsector pay, which is an important
OL,16,Fpriority to make sure public sector
OL,17,Fworkers get paid as quickly as
OL,18,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
