OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,F"But the particular outcomes that
OL,7,Fwe're hopeful we can achieve on our
OL,8,Ffirst Opposition day is, a specific
OL,9,Fcommitment from the top of the
OL,10,FExecutive that the removal of the
OL,11,Fveto, reform of the institutions so
OL,12,Fthis place can't collapse from one
OL,13,Fperson resigning, and another motion
OL,14,Fwhich creates a practical mechanism
OL,15,Ffor that, an ad hoc committee that
OL,16,Fwill come up with proposals that can
OL,17,Fbe delivered back to the Assembly by
OL,18,FSeptember and can be implemented
OL,19,Fbefore the end of this mandate."
