OL,6,FMr O'Toole said polling shows a vast
OL,7,Fmajority of people in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fwant to see Stormont reformed.
OL,10,F"We can't have a situation where one
OL,11,Fparty can collapse the institutions,"
OL,12,Fhe said.
