OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,F"Whatever the issue that they are
OL,7,Faggrieved about, and there will be
OL,8,Fissues that are difficult, that
OL,9,Fparties need to be robust about. We
OL,10,Facknowledge that, inclusive government
OL,11,Fis difficult, but you can't accept the
OL,12,Fidea that in 2024 that we can go on
OL,13,Fwith this toxic cycle of collapse and
OL,14,Frestoration. We can't allow that to
OL,15,Fhappen again."
OL,17,FMr O'Toole acknowledged that the SDLP
OL,18,Fhad a difficult election result in
OL,19,F2022 which left them without enough
OL,20,FMLAs to be entitled to a place in the
OL,21,FExecutive.
