OL,7,FOpposition had they been entitled to
OL,8,Fan Executive seat, he said: "It's a
OL,9,Fhypothetical situation, I think our
OL,10,Fstrong view would have been that
OL,11,FOpposition was an essential role for
OL,12,Fus to play whether we had qualified
OL,13,Ffor a ministry or not.
