OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,F"I think I would have been making the
OL,7,Fargument, and I think lots of my
OL,8,Fcolleagues would have agreed that it
OL,9,Fwas the right thing to be in
OL,10,FOpposition whether we had, eight,
OL,11,Fnine, 10 or 12 MLAs. We think the role
OL,12,Fof Opposition is an important and
OL,13,Fessential one, and we think it's
OL,14,Fimportant for us as a political party
OL,15,Fto set out our stall.
