OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,F"We deeply believe in protecting the
OL,7,Finstitutions, but sometimes protecting
OL,8,Fthe institutions and making politics
OL,9,Fwork here can be done better from
OL,10,FOpposition, and I think that's where
OL,11,Fwe are now.
OL,13,F"I think our role is upholding and
OL,14,Fprotecting the Good Friday Agreement,
OL,15,Fand I think we're doing that from
OL,16,Fconstructive Opposition, and I think
OL,17,Fyou'll see that on Monday with our
OL,18,Fmotions for reform. (If they're
OL,19,Fpassed), that'll be a huge achievement
OL,20,Ffor us that would prove that we're
OL,21,Fdelivering from Opposition.
