OL,3,CStormont Assembly challenged to reform
OL,4,Cand prevent future collapses
OL,6,F"We are genuinely excited and
OL,7,Fenergised by it, and I think we're
OL,8,Fdelivering a clear set of priorities
OL,9,Ffor the public in terms of holding the
OL,10,FExecutive to account in a constructive
OL,11,Fand robust way."
OL,13,FOne month in, Mr O'Toole said he
OL,14,Fbelieves they have already changed the
OL,15,Ftenure of politics.
OL,17,F"We challenged the First and deputy
OL,18,FFirst Minister on not collapsing the
OL,19,Finstitutions again, and I think people
OL,20,Fhave noticed that, and noticed the
OL,21,Fanswers that we haven't got," he said.
